tora-san goes north ( 男はつらいよ &lt;unk&gt; otoko wa tsurai yo : torajirō &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2015 japanese comedy film directed by yoji yamada . it stars kiyoshi atsumi as torajirō kuruma ( tora-san ) , and kyōko kagawa as his love interest or " madonna " . tora-san goes north is the &lt;unk&gt; entry in the popular , long-running otoko wa tsurai yo series .